<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM7.9">
<l>patiṉā ṟāmāyiravar tēvimār pārttiruppa</l>
<l>matuvāyiṟ koṇṭāṟpōl mātavaṉṟaṉ vāyamutam</l>
<l>potuvāka vuṇpataṉaip pukkunī yuṇṭakkāl</l>
<l>citaiyārō vuṉṉōṭu celvap peruñcaṅkē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As [Kṛṣṇa’s] sixteen thousand wives remain watching,</l>
<l>you begin to eat [alone] the nectar of Mādhava’s lips,</l>
<l>which [ought to] be eaten in a shared [way],</l>
<l rend="indent">as if drawing honey into the mouth,</l>
<l>If [you do so], will they not be angry with you? O greatly wealthy conch!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
